		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Tariff&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; &amp;rArr; &lt;span&gt;A tax or duty to be paid on a particular class of imports or exports.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
