	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;From the above reference, we can see that the correct combination of matching is &lt;strong&gt;A-iv, B-i, C-ii, D-iii&lt;/strong&gt;, which is given in &lt;strong&gt;Option 2&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
